  a dot in its formula, e.g. hydrated copper(II) sulfate (CuSO₄·5H₂O)."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:02.371675Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:keyword-anhydrous-salt
